_sText:
This is my very first map ever!
the goal of this map is to surf through hoops to get weapons.
there are a few secrets to this map that i think everybody will find pretty fast.
the jail has the speed mod and low gravity. 
there is a misa campo room connected to the weapon room.
when somebody goes through a hoops he/she looses all their weapons and gains the hoop's weapon and a knife.
there is 34 spawns in this map, 17 Terrorists and 17 Counter Terrorists.

its a pretty simple map but i think its pretty fun.
